This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-hw layer.

MOST IMPORTANT THE PACKAGE IS ADDED WITH NAME OF NOT THE FOLDER BUT WITH OUTPUT FILENAME
E.g HERE THE PACKAGE IS NOT ADDED AS HWLOCAL BUT AS HELLOWORLDS AS THAT IS THE OUTPUT FILE OF c PROGRAM

Dependencies
============

helloworld.c in recipes-example/hwlocal/files


Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-hw layer to your build
 II. Add IMAGE_INSTALL_append = " hwlocal" to build/conf/local.conf   //package name
 III. Build the image


I. Adding the meta-hw layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-hw'


